### Models

**`SerializationFormat`** — enum for supported output formats.

```csharp
public enum SerializationFormat
{
    Avro,
    Json,
    Protobuf
}
```

**`BootstrapperOptions`** — strongly-typed container for all CLI/config inputs.

```csharp
public class BootstrapperOptions
{
    public string Env { get; set; }
    public string Title { get; set; }
    public string Subject { get; set; }
    public string SchemaFile { get; set; }
    public string RegistryUrl { get; set; }
    public bool UpdateRegistry { get; set; }
    public SerializationFormat SerializationFormat { get; set; }
    public bool DryRun => !UpdateRegistry;
    public string FullSubject => $"{Subject}_{Env}_{Title}";
}
```

**`SchemaField`** — format-neutral representation of a single field, used internally before format-specific serialization.

```csharp
public class SchemaField
{
    public string Name { get; set; }
    public string SqlType { get; set; }   // raw SQL type from XML
    public bool Nullable { get; set; } = true;
    public bool IsRatio { get; set; } = false;
}
```

**`BuiltSchema`** — the output of a schema builder for one stat group.

```csharp
public class BuiltSchema
{
    public string StatGroupName { get; set; }
    public string SchemaContent { get; set; }   // serialized schema string (JSON or .proto)
    public SerializationFormat Format { get; set; }
}
```

